1. VICEROY / Gilded Guardian reference materials
--------------------------------------------------
The files under docs/comp-materials/ include documents describing the "Gilded
Guardian" challenge series run by the VICEROY Virtual Institute and its
partners. Ownership of those source documents remains with their respective
authors and sponsors (including Cyber Outcomes Group LLC). They are retained
