Affected files include (non-exhaustive):
  - docs/comp-materials/GILDED-GUARDIAN-EXORD.pdf
  - docs/comp-materials/GILDED-GUARDIAN-WARNORD.pdf
  - docs/comp-materials/RRII+Mantis+Design.pdf
  - docs/comp-materials/RRII Mantis Architecture.pdf
  - docs/comp-materials/RRII CYBINT-RAW-Extraction.pdf
  - docs/comp-materials/RRII-ELCOA-MANTIS.pdf

The names "VICEROY", "Gilded Guardian", "Mantis", "RRII", and related trade
